                        <interp inst="t18481127-name-629" type="given" value="GEORGE"></interp>GEORGE CAUDLK</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a scale-maker, and contract with Messrs. Shepherd to keep the scales in order—if anything wants repairing they are brought home—I never sent the prisoner for them—I do not know him.</p>
